title: Michelle Obama: Failure and rejection are a part of success
text: > Entertainment Michelle Obama: Failure and rejection are a part of success First lady Michelle Obama, speaks to welcome middle school students from the Washington area for an interactive student workshop, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015, in the State Dining Room of the White House in Washington. A concert at the White House marks 50th anniversary of the National Endowment for the Arts and Humanities. At right is Grammy award-winning blues musician Keb’ Mo’. (AP Photo/Manuel Balce Ceneta)
